txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Shimmering essence from the Dead in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'The Dead will not rise again to threaten any in this world.'
'The Dead rise and walk to the along the Kingsway. There are two types of residue left behind when they fall, and we want them both to see that they rise no more.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Shimmering Essence
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of shimmering essence.
Deliver the shimmering essence to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting shimmering essence from the Dead surrounding Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Shimmering essence from the Dead in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
